    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2009-02-04</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-02-21T18:31:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Long-Term Care and Retirement Security Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow a tax deduction from gross income for long-term care insurance premiums; (2) include long-term care insurance in employee benefit cafeteria plans and flexible spending arrangements; (3) allow a tax credit for certain long-term care costs; and (4) set forth certain consumer protections for long-term care insurance contracts. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Long-Term Care and Retirement Security Act of 2009</title>
